30:33.396 --> 30:34.963
-DON'T WORRY, I'M SURE
SHE'S AROUND HERE SOMEWHERE.

30:35.094 --> 30:36.443
-SHE'S NOT ON THE BEACH.

30:36.573 --> 30:37.923
-SUMMER HASN'T SEEN HER,

30:38.053 --> 30:39.315
AND HOBIE HASN'T
BEEN IN CLASS EITHER.

30:39.446 --> 30:40.534
-YOU'RE SURE?

30:41.056 --> 30:43.015
PHIL SAYS HE CHECKED OUT
A WAVERUNNER TO HOBIE.

30:43.145 --> 30:45.495
HOBIE SAID SUMMER WANTED
IT FOR JUNIOR GUARDS.

30:45.626 --> 30:47.846
-RON, GET A SCARAB
HERE RIGHT NOW.

30:48.759 --> 30:50.500
[BUZZER SOUNDS]

30:50.631 --> 30:53.068
[ENGINE HUMS]

30:55.766 --> 30:56.985
-I LOVE THIS!

30:57.116 --> 30:58.508
THANK YOU, HOBIE-WAN.

30:58.639 --> 31:00.336
THANK YOU FOR BRINGING ME HERE.

31:01.163 --> 31:02.773
-IT'S CALLED LOVER'S COVE.

31:02.904 --> 31:03.905
-OH?

31:04.427 --> 31:05.515
WHY DO THEY CALL IT THAT?

31:06.212 --> 31:08.910
-WELL, THERE'S A
CHURCH IN THE HILLS

31:09.476 --> 31:12.218
THAT RINGS
ITS BELLS EVERY HOUR,

31:12.348 --> 31:14.960
AND IF TWO PEOPLE KISS
WHILE THE BELLS ARE RINGING

31:15.699 --> 31:16.744
THEY STAY IN LOVE FOREVER.

31:17.658 --> 31:19.094
THAT'S THE LEGEND, ANYWAY.

31:19.834 --> 31:21.227
-WHAT DO THEY MEAN BY FOREVER?

31:22.706 --> 31:25.622
-YOU KNOW, FOREVER, ALWAYS.

31:26.667 --> 31:29.365
-ALWAYS WHILE YOU LIVE,
ALWAYS THROUGH ETERNITY,

31:29.496 --> 31:31.019
THROUGHOUT OUR LIVES, WHAT?

31:32.542 --> 31:34.675
-I DON'T KNOW, I GUESS
IT COULD MEAN THAT.

31:37.721 --> 31:39.419
-MAYBE NOW IS FOREVER, HOBIE.

31:40.289 --> 31:41.725
MEMORIES CAN BE FOREVER.

31:42.901 --> 31:44.380
MAYBE THAT'S ALL THERE IS.

31:47.688 --> 31:50.473
[SOFT MUSIC]

31:52.954 --> 31:56.305
[BELLS CHIME]

32:12.234 --> 32:17.109
[ROMANTIC MUSIC]

32:23.767 --> 32:24.812
-WOO!

32:24.943 --> 32:26.727
[SPLASH]

32:31.601 --> 32:33.212
COME ON IN, THE WATER'S GREAT.

32:33.342 --> 32:34.953
-I'D BETTER NOT.

32:39.435 --> 32:40.741
HAVE NO FEAR, PRINCESS.

32:40.871 --> 32:41.655
I'LL PROTECT YA!

32:41.785 --> 32:45.659
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

32:46.965 --> 32:48.053
[YELLS]

32:48.183 --> 32:49.576
OW!

32:57.018 --> 32:59.151
-HOBIE, STOP,
YOU'RE SCARING ME!

33:04.721 --> 33:09.204
[INTENSE MUSIC]

33:16.037 --> 33:17.169
-I DON'T SEE THEM!

33:24.263 --> 33:25.829
[SPLASHING]
-HELP!

33:26.656 --> 33:27.962
IT'S BURNING, IT'S...

33:31.183 --> 33:32.706
-HOBIE!

33:52.682 --> 33:53.988
JELLYFISH STINGS!

33:54.119 --> 33:55.772
A PORTUGUESE BATTLE WOUND.

34:07.523 --> 34:08.610
-MY HEAD!

34:09.438 --> 34:10.657
MY EARS.

34:11.266 --> 34:13.312
-WHEN I CATCH THAT BOY I'M
GONNA GROUND HIM FOR LIFE.

34:13.442 --> 34:14.878
-I'LL BET SHE'S IN LOVE.

34:15.009 --> 34:16.663
I'M SURE THEY'RE JUST
OUT CRUISING AROUND.

34:20.406 --> 34:21.581
OH, WAIT A MINUTE...

34:23.277 --> 34:24.670
LOVER'S COVE!

34:24.801 --> 34:26.150
HOBIE MUST'VE HEARD
ME TALKING TO JACKIE

34:26.281 --> 34:28.065
ABOUT TAKING YOU
TO LOVER'S COVE.

34:30.197 --> 34:31.547
I MEAN, THAT'S PROBABLY
WHERE THEY ARE.

34:32.112 --> 34:35.681
[ENGINE REVS]

34:38.598 --> 34:40.034
-I'M FREEZING.

34:40.165 --> 34:41.601
-I GOTTA GET YOU BACK
BEFORE IT GETS DARK.

34:41.731 --> 34:44.690
HOLD ON TO ME, HOBIE, HOLD ON.

34:44.821 --> 34:45.779
-LAUREN...

34:46.344 --> 34:49.348
-JUST DON'T LET GO.
-I WON'T.

34:53.743 --> 34:55.745
[SCREAMS]

35:04.667 --> 35:09.063
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

35:13.676 --> 35:15.896
HOBIE, WHERE ARE YOU?

35:23.512 --> 35:24.948
[GASPS]

35:41.269 --> 35:42.488
-THERE'S THE WAVERUNNER.

35:46.056 --> 35:47.449
-OVER HERE!

35:50.800 --> 35:53.281
HOBIE, IT'S OKAY, HOBIE.

35:53.412 --> 35:54.630
THEY FOUND US.

35:54.761 --> 35:56.066
HOBIE, YOU'LL BE OKAY.

36:01.028 --> 36:03.683
-DAD, YOU SHOULD'VE
SEEN HER OUT THERE.

36:03.813 --> 36:05.424
SHE WAS AWESOME.

36:06.164 --> 36:08.078
LAUREN'S GONNA BE
A GREAT LIFEGUARD.

36:08.209 --> 36:10.385
THEN SHE CAN WORK
RIGHT HERE AT BAYWATCH.

36:12.605 --> 36:14.041
-HOBIE, THE NEXT TIME
YOU TAKE A WAVERUNNER

36:14.172 --> 36:16.043
WITHOUT A LIFE VEST,
FORGET THE JELLYFISH.

36:16.174 --> 36:17.653
I'LL BITE YOU MYSELF, OKAY?

36:17.784 --> 36:19.089
ALL RIGHT, I GOTTA
GET OUT OF HERE.

36:19.220 --> 36:20.656
-[MUTTERS]
-I'LL SPEAK TO YOU LATER.

36:20.787 --> 36:21.875
-ALL RIGHT.

36:23.703 --> 36:24.704
DAD,

36:25.313 --> 36:27.054
CAN LAUREN HAVE DINNER
WITH US TONIGHT?

36:28.751 --> 36:30.927
-HOBIE, I THINK IT'S TIME
YOU AND I HAVE A LITTLE TALK.

36:31.058 --> 36:32.755
-I CAN COOK IF
YOU DON'T WANT TO.

36:33.582 --> 36:35.280
-LAUREN'S GOING
BACK TO PORTLAND.

36:36.324 --> 36:38.196
SHE AND HER MOM ARE
LEAVING TONIGHT.

36:38.892 --> 36:39.893
-WHY?

36:47.683 --> 36:49.076
-HOBIE, THERE'S SOMETHING
I SHOULD'VE TOLD YA

36:49.207 --> 36:50.382
WAY BEFORE THIS.

36:52.122 --> 36:53.211
-ABOUT WHAT?

36:54.342 --> 36:56.039
-LAUREN... [SIGHS]

36:56.170 --> 36:58.433
CAME HERE THROUGH THE
MAKE-A-WISH FOUNDATION.

37:00.130 --> 37:01.306
HOBIE...

37:02.698 --> 37:05.527
THEY GIVE KIDS WHO ARE SICK

37:06.267 --> 37:08.182
A CHANCE TO FULFILL A DREAM.

37:08.313 --> 37:09.618
-SICK?

37:10.619 --> 37:12.273
WHAT'RE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

37:12.404 --> 37:13.535
WHAT'S WRONG WITH HER?

37:20.063 --> 37:22.240
-HOBIE, LAUREN'S GOT
LESS THAN A YEAR TO LIVE.

37:22.892 --> 37:23.893
-WHAT?

37:25.460 --> 37:26.766
THAT'S NOT POSSIBLE!

37:26.896 --> 37:28.550
-I'M SORRY, PAL.
-WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

37:28.681 --> 37:30.248
THAT CAN'T BE TRUE!

37:30.378 --> 37:31.901
-MITCH: IT'S TRUE.

37:32.032 --> 37:33.903
-WE KISSED! IT'S FOREVER!

37:34.034 --> 37:35.165
ALWAYS!

37:35.296 --> 37:37.124
WHY ARE YOU TELLING ME THIS?

37:38.256 --> 37:39.387
[SIGHS]

37:45.959 --> 37:47.134
-LAUREN...

37:47.265 --> 37:48.440
-I NEED TO SAY
GOODBYE TO HOBIE.

37:48.570 --> 37:50.833
-HONEY, WAIT, LISTEN...
-LAUREN: MOM...

37:50.964 --> 37:52.661
I NEED TO SAY GOODBYE.

37:57.013 --> 37:58.232
[KNOCKING]

37:58.363 --> 37:59.451
HOBIE?

38:01.322 --> 38:03.672
-IF YOU WANT, I'LL TELL HER
YOU'RE TOO WEAK TO TALK.

38:03.803 --> 38:05.848
-NO.
-OKAY.

38:11.724 --> 38:12.899
HEY.

38:13.029 --> 38:14.901
-UM, COULD I PLEASE SEE HOBIE?

38:15.031 --> 38:16.337
-YEAH, SURE, BUT UH...

38:17.251 --> 38:18.687
I WANT TO THANK YOU...

38:18.818 --> 38:20.167
FOR SAVING HIM.

38:20.298 --> 38:21.908
WITHOUT YOU HE MIGHT
NOT HAVE MADE IT.

38:22.038 --> 38:25.781
-WELL, HOBIE SAVED
ME TOO, SO I GUESS...

38:26.782 --> 38:27.870
YOU KNOW.

38:28.001 --> 38:29.263
-I KNOW.

38:30.003 --> 38:31.309
WELL, GO ON, GO ON.

38:36.488 --> 38:37.532
[DOOR CLICKS]

38:40.579 --> 38:42.711
-PRINCESS LAUREN, MY RESCUER.

38:43.321 --> 38:44.539
-HOBIE-WAN.

38:44.670 --> 38:45.758
YOU OKAY?

38:45.888 --> 38:47.150
-YEAH.

38:47.281 --> 38:48.761
IT WAS JUST AN
ALLERGIC REACTION.

38:49.501 --> 38:52.199
KIND OF LIKE YOURS, I GUESS.

38:52.330 --> 38:53.461
[SIGHS]

38:54.506 --> 38:55.681
-HOBIE...

38:56.508 --> 38:58.118
I HAVE TO GO AWAY.

38:58.771 --> 39:00.163
-CAN'T YOU STAY
A LITTLE LONGER?

39:01.948 --> 39:03.776
-THANK YOU FOR TAKING
ME TO LOVER'S COVE.

39:03.906 --> 39:05.168
I'LL NEVER FORGET IT.

39:05.908 --> 39:07.170
I'LL NEVER FORGET YOU.

39:08.520 --> 39:09.782
-LAUREN, WAIT...

39:13.263 --> 39:15.004
I WANTED TO GIVE YOU SOMETHING.

39:18.312 --> 39:20.053
KIND OF, TO GUIDE YOU...

39:24.840 --> 39:26.015
WHEREVER YOU GO.

39:27.321 --> 39:28.801
-MEMORIES ARE FOREVER, HOBIE.

39:29.367 --> 39:30.846
REMEMBER ME FOREVER, OKAY?

39:34.676 --> 39:36.199
I'LL TAKE THIS
WITH ME EVERYWHERE.

39:48.864 --> 39:51.519
[SOFT MUSIC]

39:51.650 --> 39:53.086
-SO HOW'S YOUR MOM HANDLING IT?

39:53.739 --> 39:54.696
-GOOD.

39:55.349 --> 39:57.656
HER AND MITCH JUST
DECIDED TO BECOME FRIENDS.

39:57.786 --> 39:59.658
THE FEELING WAS PRETTY MUTUAL.

39:59.788 --> 40:00.876
-THAT'S GREAT.

40:02.138 --> 40:03.575
YOU THINK THEY CAN PULL IT OFF?

40:03.705 --> 40:04.837
-WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

40:06.273 --> 40:08.449
-I DON'T KNOW, SOMETIMES
IT'S HARD TO BE FRIENDS AGAIN

40:08.580 --> 40:10.146
AFTER A RELATIONSHIP
DOESN'T WORK OUT.

40:11.626 --> 40:14.629
-YOU KNOW, I THINK THE KEY
IS TO ALWAYS STAY FRIENDS.

40:14.760 --> 40:16.152
NO MATTER WHAT.

40:17.589 --> 40:18.503
-I AGREE.

40:34.910 --> 40:36.999
[SEAGULLS SQUAWK]

40:41.743 --> 40:43.571
-HEY, PAL, WHAT DO YOU SAY
WE GO GET SOME DINNER, HUH?

40:45.138 --> 40:46.008
HOBIE?

40:47.227 --> 40:48.489
-IN A MINUTE, DAD.

40:48.620 --> 40:52.319
-♪ NEVER HAVE FELT SO CLOSE TO HEAVEN

40:52.450 --> 40:54.234
♪ HERE IN YOUR ARMS

40:54.364 --> 40:56.758
♪ WE'RE NOT COMING DOWN

40:56.889 --> 40:59.631
♪ SO LET'S STOP THE CLOCK

40:59.761 --> 41:00.762
-YOU ALL RIGHT, PAL?

41:01.720 --> 41:02.851
-YEAH.

41:04.157 --> 41:05.898
JUST WATCHING THE SUN SET.

41:07.552 --> 41:12.513
♪ NOTHING CAN BREAK US APART

41:13.645 --> 41:15.777
♪ HOLDING YOUR HAND

41:16.474 --> 41:20.739
♪ HOLDING MY HEART

41:22.349 --> 41:26.658
♪ LET'S GET LOST TOGETHER

41:26.788 --> 41:29.617
♪ NEVER HAVE FELT SO CLOSE TO HEAVEN

41:29.748 --> 41:32.185
[END THEME PLAYING]
